# .gitignore for the vibepdf project (.NET 8 / WinUI 3 / MSIX-packaged)
# Scoped to this project subfolder. See the repository root .gitignore for
# solution-wide entries (e.g. .vs/).

## Build results
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

## .NET / MSBuild intermediate & generated files
project.assets.json
*.csproj.user
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.binlog
*.AssemblyAttributes.cs

## Visual Studio cache / options
.vs/
*.VC.db
*.VC.VC.opendb

## MSIX / app packaging output
AppPackages/
BundleArtifacts/
GeneratedArtifacts/
*.appx
*.appxbundle
*.appxupload
*.msix
*.msixbundle
*.cer
*.pfx
_pkginfo.txt

## Build / publish output
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
[Pp]ublish/
publish/

## Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## ReSharper / Rider
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
.idea/

## OS / editor cruft
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*~
*.swp
